uch as mounting brackets, steering boxes, and rotors; agriculture industry that include manifolds, crank cases, and PTO covers; and other industries, including pump casings, coffee pulpers, and textile machine parts. The company was formerly known as KLRF Limited and changed its name to Kovilpatti Lakshmi Roller Flour Mills Limited in May 2018. Kovilpatti Lakshmi Roller Flour Mills Limited was incorporated in 1961 and is based in Coimbatore, India."}}